<h1>Complete Guide – Breath of the Wild</h1>
<h3>Your full walkthrough for every quest, shrine, and region in Hyrule</h3>

<p>
This comprehensive walkthrough will guide you through every main quest, side quest, and shrine in 
<em>The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild</em>. Beginning on the Great Plateau, this guide helps you master 
survival mechanics, combat fundamentals, exploration techniques, and puzzle-solving skills.  
From taming horses and upgrading armor to conquering Divine Beasts and finding all 120 shrines,  
you’ll uncover every secret scattered across Hyrule.
</p>

